00:12:57.200 --> 00:13:01.670
will be what Oral Roberts saw

00:13:01.680 --> 00:13:04.150
looking at Atlas. I see Atlas, but as I'm

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:05.750
looking at it, I'm looking at this

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:07.829
thing and the Lord says, 'This is not what

00:13:07.839 --> 00:13:10.069
you're looking

00:13:10.069 --> 00:13:10.079
for.'There's

00:13:10.079 --> 00:13:12.629
something else bigger coming

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:15.910
that will shake the world and it will be

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:20.310
a sign of my Son's return.

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:22.310
There will be fearful sights that you

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:24.310
will see that will bring you to your

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:27.269
knees.

00:13:27.279 --> 00:13:29.509
For man's hearts will fail them for fear,

00:13:29.519 --> 00:13:30.629
looking after those things that are

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:33.190
coming on the earth.

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.949
And that's what we're about to see. And

00:13:34.959 --> 00:13:37.509
he talked to me today more about

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:39.910
the five shakings again:

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:42.310
there'll be a shaking in politics,

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.910
there'll be a shaking in the earth's

00:13:43.920 --> 00:13:46.230
crust, there'll be a shaking in the

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:48.550
heavens, there'll be a shaking in the

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:50.790
finances, and there'll be a shaking in

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:54.150
my church.

00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:55.990
And there'll be shakings to the point

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:59.990
where they'll all happen like labor

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:03.910
pains upon a

00:14:03.910 --> 00:14:03.920
woman—back-to-back

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:06.629
events happening all

00:14:06.639 --> 00:14:09.189
the time. Finances? 'The sky is

00:14:09.189 --> 00:14:09.199
falling.'Politics?

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:11.269
People are saying, 'What's

00:14:11.279 --> 00:14:13.110
going on?'with what we see with the

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:15.750
standoff. But the Lord said, 'I

00:14:15.760 --> 00:14:20.230
want you to pray into 2026

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:22.150
and I'll reveal things to you.'I started

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:26.069
interceding and I saw the budget.

00:14:26.079 --> 00:14:28.870
I've warned you about Trump

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:31.430
walking a pig

00:14:31.440 --> 00:14:34.230
that had makeup on, and it was the housing

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:38.949
market. And as he was walking the pig

00:14:38.959 --> 00:14:43.590
and parading the pig, this new idea,

00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:46.310
the housing market started to go up.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.310
People were excited about this new pig

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:52.310
idea, but a pig's still a pig;

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:54.389
it's not good.

00:14:54.399 --> 00:14:58.150
And he comes out after I gave this word

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:01.990
with a 50-year mortgage.

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:04.790
50-year mortgage! Oh, what a deal that

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:07.110
is; you'll pay on your house for your

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:10.790
whole life. I'm not trying to criticize because

00:15:10.790 --> 00:15:10.800
I

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:14.629
know he watches,

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:20.790
but it's just truth, sir: it's a pig.

00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:22.949
I just have to be bold and

00:15:22.959 --> 00:15:26.310
tell you the truth; it's a pig.

00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:28.870
And the Lord said the 50-year

00:15:28.870 --> 00:15:28.880
mortgage

00:15:28.880 --> 00:15:31.430
is not a good deal for the people.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:33.750
You'll pay interest for three times

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:36.310
what that house is worth over the 50

00:15:36.320 --> 00:15:37.829
years.

00:15:37.839 --> 00:15:39.829
So if you borrow a million dollars

00:15:39.839 --> 00:15:42.710
on a home, on the average house in

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:45.269
California, you're going to pay over

00:15:45.279 --> 00:15:48.870
$5 million on that house if at 7%

00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:48.880
interest—or

00:15:48.880 --> 00:15:50.710
whatever it is—you'll pay

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:53.910
over $5 million over 50 years.

00:15:53.920 --> 00:15:56.949
That's a terrible deal.

00:15:56.959 --> 00:15:59.430
But I believe it will pass and people

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:01.030
will get this going, and the banks will

00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:03.590
do this because I saw him walking in the

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:05.749
housing market, remember? And it was

00:16:05.759 --> 00:16:08.870
transparent; it wasn't solid.

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:12.069
And I saw, come January in the next

00:16:12.079 --> 00:16:13.749
two months, there was some kind of

00:16:13.759 --> 00:16:15.590
something coming, and

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:19.110
he had a golden quill in his hand,

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:20.790
and it looked like something like the

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:23.269
Declaration of Independence. There

00:16:23.279 --> 00:16:26.710
was something that he's about to sign.

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:30.150
I saw this timeframe. Now, what year is

00:16:30.160 --> 00:16:31.350
it? That's what you have to know. When

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.550
you're seeing in part, hearing in part, you

00:16:32.560 --> 00:16:34.710
don't always know what year it is, but

00:16:34.720 --> 00:16:36.710
you know it's coming. People wanted to

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:38.790
know about the hollyberry

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:41.509
bush: 'Brandon, is this the year of the

00:16:41.519 --> 00:16:43.590
major hollyberry bush, the red when the

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:46.629
angel came to you and talked to

00:16:46.629 --> 00:16:46.639
you?'I

00:16:46.639 --> 00:16:49.509
remember.

00:16:53.279 --> 00:16:55.670
It was a

00:16:55.670 --> 00:16:55.680
life-exchanging

00:16:55.680 --> 00:16:58.526
experience with the Lord. I

00:16:58.536 --> 00:16:59.670
remember everything.

00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:03.990
The angel came to me and put his hands

00:17:04.000 --> 00:17:05.350
on my lips and he said, 'Brandon, you

00:17:05.360 --> 00:17:07.110
must be still. They're not dead yet.

00:17:07.120 --> 00:17:09.429
They can't handle

00:17:09.429 --> 00:17:09.439
it.'I

00:17:09.439 --> 00:17:11.350
said, 'Well, I want to tell them about

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.590
the investments which you've given

00:17:13.590 --> 00:17:13.600
me.'And

00:17:13.600 --> 00:17:14.870
he said, 'They're not dead yet; you

00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:17.750
must be

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:17.760
still.'And

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:19.590
he said, 'Watch the hollyberry

00:17:19.590 --> 00:17:19.600
bush,'remember?

00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:21.909
And it was turning red,

00:17:21.919 --> 00:17:24.230
and the berries are red, and it was about

00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:26.549
the timeframe that a major crash would

00:17:26.559 --> 00:17:30.789
take place. And I saw the snowfall. I saw

00:17:35.039 --> 00:17:38.470
an Aston Martin in the driveway.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.909
There were things that the Lord showed me

00:17:39.919 --> 00:17:42.230
specifically, but I wrote on the copper

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:44.950
pot that was

00:17:44.950 --> 00:17:44.960
tempered—it

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:47.430
was all tattered and beat up—and I

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:49.830
wrote a name. And I can't do that

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:51.110
because everyone goes,

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:52.150
'You're trying to write the name! I know

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:53.750
what you're writing!'No, I'm not

00:17:53.760 --> 00:17:55.270
telling you what it is, because the Lord

00:17:55.280 --> 00:17:57.110
said 'no'and the angel said, 'Shh.'But I'm

00:17:57.120 --> 00:18:00.070
telling you, I saw in this

00:18:00.070 --> 00:18:00.080
timeframe,

00:18:00.080 --> 00:18:01.909
it was during the winter months, I saw a

00:18:01.919 --> 00:18:05.430
major crash. Is it this year? No, I

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:08.150
don't believe it's this year.

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:09.830
Do I believe it's because there's a lot

00:18:09.840 --> 00:18:12.230
of people who think that the economic crisis

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.830
is coming? The Lord said, 'I'm giving

00:18:13.840 --> 00:18:15.750
you a

00:18:15.750 --> 00:18:15.760
window.'This

00:18:15.760 --> 00:18:18.310
is my opinion.

00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:20.789
So if we go into a deep depression in

00:18:20.799 --> 00:18:22.230
January, you can't sit there and say,

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:23.350
'Well, you told us it was going to be

00:18:23.360 --> 00:18:25.270
great times.'That is in my opinion

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:27.750
what the Holy Spirit told me, and

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:27.760
I

00:18:27.760 --> 00:18:29.029
come on here and I pray with you and I

00:18:29.039 --> 00:18:30.230
tell you what I feel like the Lord's

00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:32.630
telling me. If it's

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:37.110
wrong, I apologize; I'm human.

00:18:37.120 --> 00:18:40.870
But I tell you by what I feel in

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:43.590
my spirit.

00:18:43.600 --> 00:18:45.510
It's me getting

00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:48.390
a perfect message

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:51.110
from an imperfect vessel. I'm only

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:53.750
perfected by his blood, and it's coming

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:57.190
through a pipe that

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:59.909
sometimes has stuff in it. I might have

00:18:59.919 --> 00:19:01.990
had a bad day,

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:03.750
you know? And people say, 'Well, that's

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:05.590
not like the people in the

00:19:05.590 --> 00:19:05.600
Bible.'And

00:19:05.600 --> 00:19:07.110
Brandon, I never claimed to be a

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:09.029
prophet;

00:19:09.039 --> 00:19:11.510
never did. People try to label

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:12.870
me that all the time. Watch

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:14.390
me; I tell you, I'm here to pray. The

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:16.150
Lord said, 'You're called to intercede.

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:18.150
Pray for the nations, Brandon.'And I do.

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:19.669
And he said, 'I'll show you what's to

00:19:19.679 --> 00:19:22.630
come and you can pray for

00:19:22.630 --> 00:19:22.640
it.'So

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:27.830
I do the best I can. I saw that

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:30.310
angel coming to me and telling me that.

00:19:30.320 --> 00:19:32.390
He said, 'And then I've warned you about

00:19:32.400 --> 00:19:34.230
a major shaking of the finances. I

00:19:34.240 --> 00:19:35.669
warned you about all these things, but

00:19:35.679 --> 00:19:37.830
the Lord said, "I'm giving you a

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:40.230
window."'And

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:42.470
a wave that's transparent will

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:46.150
happen. And I saw it come, and it was at

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:48.950
the beginning of the year. And a wave

00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:51.270
came and the finances were there. And

00:19:51.280 --> 00:19:53.270
great blessing was on the body of Christ

00:19:53.280 --> 00:19:56.310
for a window of time.

00:19:56.310 --> 00:19:56.320
It

00:19:56.320 --> 00:19:59.110
didn't last very long; the wave didn't

00:19:59.120 --> 00:20:03.029
last very long.

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:05.990
And as the ground was

00:20:05.990 --> 00:20:06.000
gold—all

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:08.150
on the gold was about that

00:20:08.150 --> 00:20:08.160
much—he

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:11.029
said, 'Fill your pockets.

00:20:11.039 --> 00:20:14.070
Fill your pockets.

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:15.669
For there's not much there, but it's

00:20:15.679 --> 00:20:18.390
enough to get you in the overflow for

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:20.710
what's coming, for a great storm is

00:20:20.710 --> 00:20:20.720
coming.'A

00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:23.750
great storm is coming, and he

00:20:23.760 --> 00:20:25.430
still talks about that storm almost

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:28.070
every day,

00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:31.350
warning me, keeping me on track, praying

00:20:31.360 --> 00:20:34.070
in the spirit. So, this is what I have

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:37.270
for you today. I saw a major political

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:45.430
figure in Israel be taken out.

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:48.950
It will shake the nation.

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:57.750
I saw old faces coming back

00:20:57.760 --> 00:21:01.110
because of this man. A great shaking is

00:21:01.120 --> 00:21:04.149
coming. The Lord said the third temple will be

00:21:04.159 --> 00:21:07.350
negotiated soon.

00:21:07.350 --> 00:21:07.360
There

00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:09.830
will be

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:15.909
an acceleration of things in Israel with

00:21:15.919 --> 00:21:19.190
my people.

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:21.190
But I can't say that word. He said,

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:23.804
'Be still no

00:21:23.814 --> 00:21:30.070
more.'You

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:31.270
know, when you're on live

00:21:31.270 --> 00:21:31.280
and

00:21:31.280 --> 00:21:32.789
I have to watch what I say. The

00:21:32.799 --> 00:21:34.549
Lord said there will be things that I tell

00:21:34.559 --> 00:21:36.710
you from now on that you're

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:38.149
not going to be able to talk about

00:21:38.159 --> 00:21:41.110
everything anymore.

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:47.510
But we must pray now

00:21:47.520 --> 00:21:52.549
for Black Friday,

00:21:52.559 --> 00:21:56.390
specifically about the Mall of America

00:21:56.390 --> 00:21:56.400
and

00:21:56.400 --> 00:21:59.190
the

00:21:59.200 --> 00:22:04.230
Atlanta airport.

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:05.830
You can have a list of things to pray

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:10.070
for; the Mall of America and Atlanta

00:22:10.070 --> 00:22:10.080
are

00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:14.070
very serious, especially the airport.

00:22:23.039 --> 00:22:26.149
New Year's Eve, of course, Times Square.

00:22:26.159 --> 00:22:29.430
Do you

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:31.750
know where the two

00:22:31.760 --> 00:22:35.750
men stand in Times Square

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:39.110
on CNN?

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:44.789
They stand

00:22:44.799 --> 00:22:47.510
on a platform, but their backs are

00:22:47.520 --> 00:22:51.350
facing the ball

00:22:51.360 --> 00:22:54.310
on this side.

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:01.029
Can you tell me their names, please,

00:23:01.039 --> 00:23:11.029
son?

00:23:11.039 --> 00:23:19.990
He works for CNN, and the other guy is from Bravo.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:21.270
It doesn't matter; they're

00:23:21.280 --> 00:23:24.390
gay.

00:23:24.400 --> 00:23:25.270
This is

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:27.750
Anderson Cooper and

00:23:27.760 --> 00:23:30.070
Andy

00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:32.310
Cohen,

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:34.630
whatever his name is.

00:23:37.120 --> 00:23:41.430
Over on this side, there's a building

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:45.270
right here. Midway up, there is something

00:23:45.280 --> 00:23:49.669
that happens in that building.

00:23:56.480 --> 00:23:59.510
There is a flash, a light that

00:23:59.520 --> 00:24:01.669
will come from there if we don't

00:24:01.679 --> 00:24:03.669
pray. You say, 'Well, Brandon, that's a

00:24:03.669 --> 00:24:03.679
cop-out.'No,

00:24:03.679 --> 00:24:05.110
I'm telling you what I see

00:24:05.120 --> 00:24:08.710
in these visions.

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:11.590
But I saw a flash. What year? I don't

00:24:11.600 --> 00:24:15.029
know. Because of that man—do you know

00:24:15.039 --> 00:24:15.909
who I'm talking about?

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.870
The guy that just won.

00:24:22.240 --> 00:24:24.070
The man that just

00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:24.080
won—oh,

00:24:24.080 --> 00:24:24.950
Mayor

00:24:24.950 --> 00:24:24.960
Mamdani.

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:28.549
If he stands on the platform in January—this

00:24:28.549 --> 00:24:28.559
is

00:24:28.559 --> 00:24:30.390
the

00:24:30.390 --> 00:24:30.400
timeframe

00:24:30.400 --> 00:24:31.909
because he was

00:24:31.919 --> 00:24:34.390
standing on the platform greeting the

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:36.390
people.

00:24:36.400 --> 00:24:39.430
He was there when this flash took place.

00:24:39.440 --> 00:24:41.669
So if he's there in January, we

00:24:41.679 --> 00:24:43.669
really pray about this. But if it's next

00:24:43.679 --> 00:24:46.230
year, I don't know. I see sometimes

00:24:46.240 --> 00:24:49.190
years in advance;

00:24:49.200 --> 00:24:50.789
sometimes I see it right in front of

00:24:50.799 --> 00:24:52.789
your face. This is seeing

00:24:52.789 --> 00:24:52.799
in

00:24:52.799 --> 00:24:54.630
part

00:24:54.630 --> 00:24:54.640
and

00:24:54.640 --> 00:24:57.350
hearing in part, but I saw his

00:24:57.360 --> 00:24:58.950
face.

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:03.029
He's the one that pushes down the thing

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:07.669
that makes the ball go, and

00:25:11.760 --> 00:25:14.950
as they sing that song, that flash took

00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:17.190
place.

00:25:17.200 --> 00:25:19.750
Now, why would the Muslim Brotherhood

00:25:19.760 --> 00:25:21.669
want to take out a Muslim? I don't know.

00:25:21.679 --> 00:25:23.029
That's why I don't understand everything

00:25:23.039 --> 00:25:31.510
I see, but I saw his face.

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.830
Maybe it's not

00:25:33.840 --> 00:25:37.350
Braden because I saw Ukraine.

00:25:37.360 --> 00:25:39.350
What if it's not terrorists like that? Do

00:25:39.360 --> 00:25:41.190
you understand? I see in part. Do you

00:25:41.200 --> 00:25:43.350
remember I said I saw an arrow

00:25:43.350 --> 00:25:43.360
go

00:25:43.360 --> 00:25:45.669
to Ukraine, back to Russia,

00:25:45.679 --> 00:25:47.669
and back like this?

00:25:51.760 --> 00:25:53.269
I thought

00:25:53.279 --> 00:25:55.830
about that when I just said that.

00:25:57.760 --> 00:25:59.909
I piece everything together in my

00:25:59.919 --> 00:26:02.070
natural mind, which is

00:26:02.070 --> 00:26:02.080
often

00:26:02.080 --> 00:26:03.750
dangerous because you shouldn't add to or

00:26:03.760 --> 00:26:05.269
take away from anything the Lord shows

00:26:05.279 --> 00:26:08.789
you. But you try to make sense of it. I

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:13.669
start going, 'Well, Lord, why

00:26:13.679 --> 00:26:15.669
would they try to hurt their

